{"tid":398294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【若蓮喪子 ‧ 頭七】今日LUNCH食菜肉包 + 蓮蓉包慶祝！","createTime":"2017-09-13T05:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T08:53:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea55ae9ce9bb7b8381b326284e6c3a7ea3d12369","tid":398294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"每年9月6日定為「天滅賣港賊日」, 即為香港新傳統節日, 傳統食品係菜肉包 + 蓮蓉包<br />\n<br />\n同西方愚人節一樣, 係呢日係可以對賣港賊10級涼薄及冷血, 而不受道德指責<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/8fxgzy815/LUNCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2F8fxgzy815%2FLUNCH.jpg&h=0712f4fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4548bb3d3ae1e195d5cc98492d897b05d9ff4f2","tid":398294,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解買兩個既"},{"pid":"5df49ad061464e76dd0a536b86903e1921d95179","tid":398294,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"今日咁熱<br />\n係要涼薄下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c66832f8cf64fc829587820378adce9c3ae358","tid":398294,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:42:57.000Z","msg":"丁酉年秋，酷吏若蓮長子自盡，民不以為悲，反竊喜。吏斥眾禽獸，民怒詰之：「昔吏行峻法，先生棄世，學子尋短，死者甚眾，何不以悲！吏不思過而自省，反諷泉下師生，豈亦非獸乎！十數載前，先有羅門范氏嘲先生之亡，曰：「若為苛政故，亡者豈止一二耶？」；及至學子歿者逾七十眾，更悉九日連殞七命者。吏吳克儉又譏其事，曰：「生徒尋死，蓋因未嘗遠謀，於未未規之，故取死之道矣。」二吏身居朝堂，掌司徒事，見師生死，冷嘲熱諷，何鮮仁也！今若蓮喪子，吏偽憐之，更未憐昔眾師生。民仇吏而悅，喜見其悲，不亦人性邪？非子曰：『以直報怨，以德報德』邪？先有不仁之官，後有無情之民。百姓受苦，師生洩恨。喜見官悲，樂其兒亡。揮毫成句，賀其早喪！今日之事，豈非無因？所謂因果，當如此狀。師生自戕，酷吏未助，反笑諸子，自問其過。如今吏悲，斥我無情。早知今日，何必當初！！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kZfFpjM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkZfFpjM.jpg&h=1e3949c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1adee2dad8c7d7353957a73edf1c895250563e77","tid":398294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gYxAPov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgYxAPov.jpg&h=987996f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb318d52104fe731d73285a41a105e571caf3921","tid":398294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170907/_2017090722560339451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170907%2F_2017090722560339451.jpg&h=284b9ace&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64abab9f7d643aa426044e411805d50bd740c481","tid":398294,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解買兩個既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係就買多兩個喇<br />\n咁高興"},{"pid":"058ada787803fdef57e428d6d237206f5c4fda7e","tid":398294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:50:53.000Z","msg":"今晚返屋企整「蒻蓮桑子」甜品食！"},{"pid":"e7b02161f976abd32175f4f9a14a1aa3c1656496","tid":398294,"uid":92442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"菜肉蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72990d5654e453c0fd23134acc09c6564ce6a49","tid":398294,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"你地真係好顛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade8397b11ab720774184d471093b841c301cede","tid":398294,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"